<h4>Proverbs: 12.12</h4><br>The wicked desireth the net of evil men: but the root of the righteous yieldeth fruit.
***
<h4>Proverbs: 12.13</h4><br>The wicked is snared by the transgression of his lips: but the just shall come out of trouble.
***
<h4>Proverbs: 12.14</h4><br>A man shall be satisfied with good by the fruit of his mouth: and the recompence of a man's hands shall be rendered unto him.
