***
<h4>Proverbs: 17.18</h4><br>A man void of understanding striketh hands, and becometh surety in the presence of his friend.
***
<h4>Proverbs: 17.19</h4><br>He loveth transgression that loveth strife: and he that exalteth his gate seeketh destruction.
***
<h4>Proverbs: 17.20</h4><br>He that hath a froward heart findeth no good: and he that hath a perverse tongue falleth into mischief.
***
