<h4>Proverbs: 17.27</h4><br>He that hath knowledge spareth his words: and a man of understanding is of an excellent spirit.
***
<h4>Proverbs: 17.28</h4><br>Even a fool, when he holdeth his peace, is counted wise: and he that shutteth his lips is esteemed a man of understanding.
